content:
[[include :scp-wiki-cn:theme:basalt darkmode=a|hidetitle=a]]

[[include :etinjat:typeface-cn
|Huiwen-mincho=true
]]

[[module css]]

@import url("https://fonts.googleapis.com/css2?family=Trade+Winds&display=swap");

:root {
  --rate-module-background-color: 16, 50, 50;
}

#header h1 a::before {
    display: none;
}

#header h1 a span::after {
    margin-bottom: 0;
}

#container {
  width: 100%;
  margin: 0px;
  background: linear-gradient(to bottom, #102329 105vh, #000000);
}

#container #header {
  background: none;
  position: absolute;
  box-shadow: unset;
  backdrop-filter: none;
}

/* ---- DIVS ---- */

.banner {
  background-image: linear-gradient(to bottom, #00000000 95%, #102329 100%), linear-gradient(to top, #00000000 95%, #102329 100%), url("http://scp-wiki.wikidot.com/local--files/masks-of-nyarlathotep-hub/temple.jpeg");
  color: white;
  text-align: center;
  width: 100vw !important;
  max-width: 100vw !important;
  height: 100vh;
  position: relative;
  left: calc(-50dvw + 50%);
  background-repeat: no-repeat;
  background-size: cover;
  background-position: top;
  margin-top: -2.70em;

  /* align contents to center */
  display: flex;
  justify-content: center;
  align-items: center;
}

.title {
  font-family:Huiwen-mincho, sans-serif;
  font-size: 6em;
  font-weight: bold;
  padding-left: 10px;
  padding-right: 10px;
  padding-top: 20px;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px black);
}

.heading {
  font-size: 2.5em;
  font-family:Huiwen-mincho, sans-serif;
}

.overlay {
  filter: blur(10px);
}

.denied {
  transform: rotate(15deg);
  color: red;
  font-size: 3em;
  font-family: Sofia Sans;
  font-weight: bold;
  z-index: 3;
  height: 0;
  position: relative;
  filter: drop-shadow(0 0 10px #00000077);
}

.darkdocument {
  background-color: #00000033 !important;
}

/* ---- TEXT COLORS ---- */

a {
  color: #00CED1 !important;
}

a:hover {
  color: #20B2AA;
}

a:visited {
  color: #008B8B;
}

::selection {
  background-color: #103232;
}


/* ---- FOR MOBILE DEVICES ---- */

@media only screen and (max-width: 767px) {

.title {
  font-size: 4em;
}

[[/module]]

[[div class="banner"]]

[[span class="title"]]奈亚拉托提普的面具[[/span]]

[[/div]]

@@ @@

[[=]]

[[div class="darkdocument"]]

//有一种恐怖，我几乎不敢提及它；因为我的理智告诉我，只有我一个人能看到它。它早已死去，然而却日复一日地通过吸取时间和血液，像吸血鬼一样繁荣生长，它吸取的时间和血液越多，活得就越久，甚至超过了那些最初喂养它的人。//

//当我不停地目视灵魂试图离开它们的肉体时，我意识到这种恐怖导致了我曾经所知的世界的死亡，尽管一个新的世界正在挣扎着诞生。现在，我害怕在一个充满怪物和受害者的世界里，疯狂将成为夜晚降临的指向，以便我们能够再次看到光明——那微弱的希望之光，期盼着驱逐这些寄生虫。//

//双刃剑的时代下，乐观主义主宰着我们的意志，而悲观主义主宰着我们的心灵；这是不断增长的时代，如癌症般恐怖的机械。//

[[/div]]

